---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Arkhe Branding - Branding & Marketing for Home Services Businesses";
const description = "Comprehensive research on branding strategies, marketing approaches, and brand development for home services businesses and contractors.";
const canonicalURL = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site);
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalURL={canonicalURL}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Arkhe Branding</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Research-Backed Branding for Home Services</p>
      <p class="subtitle">Explore evidence-based branding strategies, marketing approaches, and brand development for home services businesses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="featured-topic">
    <h2>Featured Topic: Branding & Marketing for Home Services Businesses</h2>
    <p>Discover how to build a strong brand for your home services business. Understand branding principles, marketing strategies, and customer acquisition approaches tailored to the home services industry.</p>
    <div class="pillar-cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/">Overview</a></h3>
        <p>Introduction to branding for home services, key principles, and how strong branding drives customer acquisition and loyalty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/history/">History & Evolution</a></h3>
        <p>Trace the evolution of home services marketing from traditional methods through digital transformation and modern strategies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/technical-deep-dive/">Technical Deep-Dive</a></h3>
        <p>Explore brand architecture, positioning frameworks, visual identity systems, and digital marketing infrastructure for home services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/ontology/">Ontology & Knowledge Base</a></h3>
        <p>Comprehensive taxonomy of branding concepts, marketing channels, customer journey stages, and home services industry terminology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/trends/">Current Trends & Future Outlook</a></h3>
        <p>Emerging trends: local SEO, reputation management, video marketing, and AI-powered customer acquisition in home services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/tools/">Tools & Resources</a></h3>
        <p>Brand assessment frameworks, marketing ROI calculators, and resources for building effective home services brands.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3><a href="/home-services-branding/challenges/">Common Challenges & Solutions</a></h3>
        <p>Address common branding challenges in home services with evidence-based solutions and proven strategies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About This Site</h2>
    <p>Arkhe Branding is dedicated to providing research-backed, comprehensive resources on branding and marketing for home services businesses. Our content is grounded in branding theory, marketing research, and practical industry experience.</p>
    <p>Whether you're a home services contractor building your brand, a marketing professional serving the industry, or a business owner seeking to grow through better branding, you'll find evidence-based insights and practical guidance here.</p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .featured-topic {
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .featured-topic h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .featured-topic > p {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .pillar-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .card h3 a {
      color: #667eea;
    }

    .card h3 a:hover {
      color: #764ba2;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .about {
      background: #f0f4ff;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .about h2 {
      color: #667eea;
    }

    .about p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .pillar-cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
